Valdosta State University cancelled classes on Friday ahead of a rally in support of flag supporters . 
  Michelle Manhart , 38 , was arrested last week after she refused to return an American flag to demonstrators who had walked on it to protest racism . 
  She was banned from campus and police found a gun on one of the demonstrators . 
  Police said they traced the gun to a protester who was part of the flag-walking demonstration . 
  Flag supporters gathered at the university in Valdosta on Friday . 
 